minios-tools (1.4.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Refactor sb2iso script to automatically detect bootloader type and simplify
    usage
  * Update help messages and examples

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Thu, 28 Aug 2025 15:45:25 +0300

minios-tools (1.4.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add support for the latest MiniOS ISO format to sb2iso
  * Improve apt2sb, script2sb, chroot2sb:
    - Make overlay mount more reliable by setting
      LIBMOUNT_FORCE_MOUNT2=always and adjusting mount arguments
    - Enable strict shell options (set -euo pipefail) so the
      script fails fast on errors and unset variables
    - Fix and harden trap/umount/rmdir to avoid leaving temporary
      directories or mounted points behind
  * Remove `minios-kernelpack`. Its functions are now performed by
    `minios-kernel` and `minios-kernel-manager`
  * Add Indonesian translation
  * Update translations

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Mon, 11 Aug 2025 09:10:29 +0300

