    MiniOS ISO format, fixed some bugs, impruved user experience.
  * Update apt2sb script to version 1.2.1. Fixed building with overlayfs.
  * Update script2sb script to version 1.2.1. Fixed building with overlayfs.
  * Update chroot2sb script to version 1.0.1. Fixed building with overlayfs.
  * Update sb script to version 1.0.1. Ajusted compatibility with MiniOS 5.0.

